hackathonVoting.tipsModalTitle: As a voter in this hackathon, I commit to upholding the principles of fairness, integrity, and respect. I agree to:
hackathonVoting.tipsModaltext1: I will evaluate each project based on its innovation, technical execution, impact, and presentation quality, without bias or favoritism.
hackathonVoting.tipsModaltext2: I will honor the hard work and creativity of all participants, ensuring each project receives fair consideration.
hackathonVoting.tipsModaltext3: I will vote truthfully, refraining from any dishonest behavior such as multiple voting or influencing others to vote unethically.
hackathonVoting.tipsModaltext4: I will foster a positive and inclusive environment through my voting, contributing to the spirit of collaboration and mutual respect.
hackathonVoting.tipsModalTitle5: By agreeing to these principles, I pledge to vote ethically and fairly.
